  "title": "Part Time Piano Teacher (Freelance)",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking dedicated Part Time Piano Teachers who are eager to kick start their teaching journey. <br /></p><p><strong>Location:</strong><br /><br />BoonKeng / Hougang / SengKang</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong><br /><br />Minimum Practical Grade 8 qualification</p><p>Minimum Music Theory Grade 5 qualification</p><p>Individuals with a strong sense of commitment, discipline and responsibility</p><p>Patient, energetic, and cheerful personality</p><p>Passion for teaching children in both individual and in group settings<br /></p><p><u>Must be able to travel. Travel allowance will be provided.</u></p><p><strong>Work Schedule:</strong><br /><br />Wednesday & Saturday (April start)</p><p><br />New Teachers who are keen to be part of the piano teaching community are welcome to join! Training will be provided. </p><p>Interested candidates are invited to submit their resume to huckleberrymusicschool@gmail.com.</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted for an interview and a demonstration of their teaching / playing skills is required.</p>",
